        <updateDate>2012-03-30T23:13:37Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Honors Theodor Geisel (Dr. Seuss) for his success in encouraging children to discover the joy of reading.</p> <p>Honors the 14th anniversary of Read Across America Day, which occurs on March 2, 2012.</p> <p>Encourages parents to read with their children for at least 30 minutes on Read Across America Day.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Encouraging people in the United States to recognize March 2, 2012, as Read Across America Day.</title>
